{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "展梦白在炼箭窟中与蛇面人及众黑衣人展开激战，以铁剑大开杀戒，连毙数人。蛇面人不敌败走，展梦白追击时被黑袍人拦截。黑袍人以黑衣人为盾牌，展梦白投鼠忌器，二人转为徒手相搏。黑袍人巧言拖延，暗中触发机关放出妙龄少女，欲令其释放毒气。高挑少女挺身反抗，拒绝助纣为虐。黑袍人见大势已去，趁展梦白分神之际逃入铜门。关键时刻蓝大先生赶到，告知展梦白其结义大哥杨某多次设计害他，并已将杨某斩杀。二人联手破开铜门，发现黑袍人已从暗道逃走。展梦白在崖上遇见铁驼，两位前辈老友重逢，嬉笑怒骂间约定再战一场。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇面人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好大胆的奸细，难为你是如何混入来的，只是你又何必苦苦混入这里送死！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇面人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还等什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是被他们逼来的，快快站开一边，要送死的，便也快些过来。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "双刀客",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看刀。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇面人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怯敌不攻，凌迟处死。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好，你们很好。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们倒还有兴趣活下去么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "且慢。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你要怎样？",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "你为何要他们死？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "莫非你还有心要救他们？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "这倒怪了，你杀死了将近二十人，却要救这六人，难道这六人与别人有何不同？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "你为何……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我为何要留下他们，让你逼取口供。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "逼取你的口供，也是一样。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "轻些，死人逼不出口供来的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "失陪。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你杀吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "你纵不动手，我也要杀你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你手握利剑，我却是赤手空拳，这种手如何动法，你要杀尽管杀吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "我若不用兵刃，又当如何？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你若不用兵刃，我便好好与你拼上一拼，生死胜负，各凭武功，谁也怨不得谁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "但我劝你，还是不要抛剑的好。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "好无耻的奴才！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你不用剑，我来用剑，这道理岂非公平得很，有何无耻？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘们，快出来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快到我房中去拍动狼尾，将毒气放出来。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有我缠住这厮，你们怕什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tiao_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "高挑少女",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "毒气攻出，岂非连咱们也一齐死了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_gao_tiao_shao_nv",
      "text": "傻丫头，只要这厮倒下去，我不会去救你们么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tiao_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "高挑少女",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "我姐妹们虽然也不是良家妇人，但自从被你们骗买来这里后，早已受得够了，我们也不愿一辈子这样过活，早已想出去逛逛了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_gao_tiao_shao_nv",
      "text": "我锦衣玉食地养着你们，有什么对不起你们，你竟敢如此说法，莫非不要命了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tiao_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "高挑少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "反正你也要死了，我也不必再怕你，这位相公你放心，咱们姐妹绝不害你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "text": "多行不义必自毙，你若是束手就缚，有问必答，展梦白或许还不伤你性命！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展梦白，原来你便是展梦白。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展梦白呀展梦白，你今日纵破了此地，也不必得意，这只是你大运当头，又岂是你的本领？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我此番说来，你心里只怕还在不服，只当这里人都是你真刀真枪杀死的，哪有什么运气，嘿嘿，你若真的如此想法，便大大错了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "第一，只因我等自恃这里极为隐秘，是以未曾布下消息机关。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "第二，在这里炼箭之人，一入此窟，便被我搜去了身上的迷香与暗器，免得他们乘隙背叛，或是争风吃醋，哪知却便宜了你，这些下五门的贼子，武功虽不高，但迷香暗器，却各有独到手法，他们若有暗器在身，岂容你如此轻易杀死？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "第三、催梦草不来，炼箭只得停顿，而外面索箭甚急，我只得将洞中存箭全部运了出去，若有情人箭在，你只怕早已变作刺猬，而炼箭若不停，炉火若不灭，你若剑劈铜鼎，便躲不过炉中的毒烟毒火，何况，炉火若在，毒气便有储存，我方才在里面，便早已将毒气放出来了，根本不必等到现在，再令那些贱人去动手，此刻只怕你早已中毒毙命了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你这不是运气是什么……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "原来那房里还有条出口。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小兄弟，你果然在这里。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小兄弟，老夫找得你好苦。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "前辈，晚辈只当再难见着你了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小兄弟，你放心，老天毕竟还有些公道，不会叫你这种人死的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好，干得好，干得痛快，一年不见，想必小兄弟你武功又精进了许多。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "运气，哈哈，不错，正是运气，若是黄衫人那酸老儿在这里，只怕便要劝你日后行事要小心些了。若是运气不来，又当如何，但老夫却要告诉你，尽管放开胆量，向前闯去就是了，运气若是来了，打都打不走的，想老夫当年又何尝不是你这样天不怕地不怕的脾气，到今日却也活得好好的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "前辈能寻到此处，莫非是见着了我大哥么？他想必知道……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "谁是你的大哥？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "便是杨……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "大哥，好一个大哥，你拜了他做大哥，当真算是你的运气到了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "大哥对我，确是不错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不错不错，的确不错。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "难道……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "还难道什么？他三番两次地要害死你，你却还要口口声声唤他做大哥。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "前辈只怕是误会了吧？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你还不懂？你可要我说出来么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "不必说了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "为何不说，他第一次将你骗去昆仑双绝之处，想借那两个老儿之手将你除去。第二次又寻来些催梦草，偷偷要你服下，哪知却偏偏解了你的火毒，于是他一计不成，再施二计，便将你骗来这里，哪知你傻人却有傻福，连炼魂潭水都淹不死你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "前辈你怎会知道的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "老夫自然已遇着他了，他虽然满腹诡计，但老夫只要略施手法，便逼出了他的实话，否则老夫又怎能寻来这里。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "他此刻怎样了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "老样子，还不是被老夫一刀砍下了脑袋，难道老夫还要留下这样的弟子来败坏门风么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但望前辈能容弟子将他尸首掩埋，也不枉我与他结拜一场。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "门里还有鬼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 503,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "铜门虽厚，却也挡不住老夫这一锤，小兄弟，且看老夫进门捉鬼。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "何必前辈动手，有事弟子本该服其劳的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小兄弟，你也行么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "大约可以。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好好，快让老夫看看你的手段。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好剑！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好剑！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "果然好剑，小兄弟，站开一边，瞧老夫的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好锤！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "锤虽不好，老夫的手却不错。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你管左面的，老夫管右面，看看到底是剑快还是锤快？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 549,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "那边啥也没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 557,
      "line_end": 557
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "瞧瞧这边。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 559,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "快退！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "外面的女子无辜，前辈何妨也赐给她们些解毒丸药，在下可以屏息许久，倒可不必用它。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 565,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你总是先想着别人再想自己。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 569,
      "line_end": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "原来那房里还有条出口。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 579,
      "line_end": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "想必有人自那山石逃去，又断了通路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "他逃得好快。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 585,
      "line_end": 585
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这鬼地方当真呆不得了，快走吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 587,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "妙龄少女们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你们……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 589,
      "line_end": 589
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要求了，咱们走了，少不得也要带你们走的，好教你们再出去迷人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "妙龄少女们",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "没有迷人，我们没有……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 595
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们手拉着手，一个接一个跟着老夫走，知道么？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 599
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小兄弟，爬绳子的把戏你玩过么？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 603,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "弟子还可上去，但那些女子……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你可怜她们，便将她们一个一个抱上去就是。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 607,
      "line_end": 607
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这个……这个……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 609
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你先抱重的，再抱轻的，切切要抱得紧些，若是掉下一个，岂非可惜了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 613
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "其实本该老前辈……唉，前辈若不肯，弟子只有……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 615,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小兄弟莫要怕，咱们上去了，自有人设法下来接她们。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 617,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 621,
      "line_end": 621
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "老夫一生，最大的毛病就是怕做事，除非万不得已，走路时总要带几个徒弟的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 625
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "妙极妙极……前辈先请吧！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 627,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你先上，掉下来老夫还可接着。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 629,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "蓝老儿，是你么，快些上来，老夫在这里等了你许久了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 645,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "前辈怎会来到这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 657,
      "line_end": 657
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "老夫被你耽误，再也追不着那厮，便换家客栈去问，想去找你聊聊，幸好那城里客栈不多，但老夫虽寻着了庙，却跑了和尚，你早已走了，只剩下那店小二在骂你，骂得狗血淋头。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 659,
      "line_end": 659
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "本该骂的，若是换了我，只怕骂得更厉害。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 663,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你倒老实得很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 667
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "前辈是否问出弟子的去向，才赶来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 669,
      "line_end": 669
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不错，我赶来这里，未寻着你，却先见到他们，老夫一见他们的衣衫，便知道是蓝老儿的徒弟。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 671,
      "line_end": 671
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "原来两位前辈本乃相识。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 675,
      "line_end": 675
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不但相识，老夫还想念他得很。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 677,
      "line_end": 677
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "驼老儿，你想我，我也在想你呀！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 679,
      "line_end": 681
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好老儿，手脚倒还蛮快的嘛，老夫还只当你已老掉牙了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 683,
      "line_end": 685
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "牙还在，可要我咬你一口试试？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 687,
      "line_end": 687
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好老鬼，想不到你还是如此贫嘴，老夫只当你这张嘴已烂光了哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 689,
      "line_end": 691
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "咱们多年不见，也该庆祝庆祝才是。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 695,
      "line_end": 695
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "多少？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 697,
      "line_end": 697
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "三天。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 701,
      "line_end": 701
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "好，三天就三天，你吃得消么？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 703,
      "line_end": 703
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你胆敢瞧不起老夫，只怕先躺下的是你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 705,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 711,
      "line_end": 711
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "寻个隐僻所在，你我好好的……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 713,
      "line_end": 713
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "喝酒何必要隐僻之地？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 715,
      "line_end": 715
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "谁要喝酒？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 717,
      "line_end": 717
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "那……那……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 719,
      "line_end": 719
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小兄弟，你只当他要与我喝酒么？哈哈，这老儿数十年前败在老夫手下，如今心里还在不服，要好生寻我再打上一架。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 721,
      "line_end": 725
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁驼",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "当真是恶狗不忘千年臭，数十年之事，你居然还记得。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 727,
      "line_end": 729
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "你若不记得，为何要来寻老夫？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 731,
      "line_end": 731
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小兄弟，那日你看老夫打了一架，今日可还要看看，只是，这一次只怕不及那次精彩了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 735,
      "line_end": 737
    }
